Tactics

Use knowledge and skills at the best time and in the most advantageous way

Stake up and sell
Stake coins as they increase in value, then sell at the top
Go
Borrow USD don't Lend
USD doesn't appreciate in value, paid-back USD have less value than lent-out USD
Savings, pensions, bonds are all forms of lending
FED is number one USD borrower and will ensure USD borrowers always win
Go
Make down and draw
Provide liquidity (Moneymake) as coins decrease in value, then draw out the coins at the bottom.
Go
Borrow before an uptrend (ANCHOR)
Borrow UST and deposit bLuna for collateral, its price goes up and your LTV goes down
Go
Payback before a downtrend (ANCHOR)
Payback UST and withdraw bLuna so you can sell before it drops
Go
